# Data cleaning
-- Replace NULL card numbers with a readable label
UPDATE coffee_sales
SET card_number = COALESCE(card_number, 'Paid by Cash');

-- Remove 'R' currency symbol and extra spaces
UPDATE coffee_sales
SET transaction_amount =
    TRIM(REPLACE(transaction_amount, 'R', ''));

-- Convert transaction amount from VARCHAR to NUMERIC
ALTER TABLE coffee_sales
ALTER COLUMN transaction_amount
TYPE NUMERIC(10,2)
USING CAST(transaction_amount AS NUMERIC(10,2));

The data was already clean overall; it only needed those changes.
